t-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州位于中国南部，珠江三角洲的北缘，是中国最发达的城市之一。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这里是粤食之乡、购物天堂，文化交汇之地，也是一座历史与现代感并存的“南国之城”。作为中国最早开埠的通商口岸，广州一直保持着较好的通商氛围，这也令城市的发展愈加迅速。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">每条街道都灯火辉煌，处处充满着令人迷醉的魅力。无论是沙面建筑群中精美的欧洲古典建筑，还是那些具有岭南韵味的商业骑楼，甚至是夜晚珠江沿岸的绚烂夜色，都会让你深深的爱上这座四季如春的南方都市。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">9-12月</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州的冬季较短，夏季较长。终年温暖湿润，温差也较小。雨季一般集中在春夏两季，最佳旅行时间为秋季及初冬时节。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">1-2月：&nbsp;这两个月为广州的冬季，年均气温最低，为14度左右。虽然不会有明显的降雨，但是湿冷的天气还是令人倍感阴凉。如果赶上春节时期，从广州前往各地的机票及火车票都十分紧张，如果有计划春节前往广州的游客，返程票一定要提前买好。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3-5月：&nbsp;3-5月为广州的春季，气温回升至20度上下，虽然气温回暖但却迎来了连绵不断的阴雨季。这期间广州的天气阴沉并时常伴有降雨，虽然雨势不大但一下就是几天。春季期间广州旅游进入淡季，来广州游玩的游客不多，各酒店都会纷纷打出优惠的价格来争抢客源。如果你喜欢游览人少时的景点同时又不介意小雨相伴，春季则更为适合你。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">6-8月：&nbsp;6-8月广州进入夏季，气温维持在30度上下，略感闷热。夏季同时还是广州的台风季，虽然台风不会频繁光临，但偶遇一次也会让旅行体验大打折扣，游客在出行前最好提前查阅天气预报，做好应对工作。夏季广州进入了暑期的旅游热潮，游客多以学生流为主。机票及酒店会有一定程度的上调。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">9-12月：&nbsp;秋季和初冬最适合来广州玩。对于广州多雨的天气来说，这几个月可谓是晴空万里，非常适宜户外活动。气温维持在24度左右，体感舒适。这几个月也是广州的旅游旺季，许多来自北方的游客选择到广州来避寒。秋季又正值广州各大商场、批发市场换季打折期，吸引了大批来广州淘货的游客。此时间段往来广州的机票及酒店均会有一定程度的上浮，游客最好提前两到三个月预定。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">建议游玩天数</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">3-4天</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州大多数的景点都集中在主城区及珠江沿线。就连越秀公园和白云山这种能与大自然亲近的风景区也紧挨着北部城区。游玩广州市区的景点游客大致会花上1-2天的时间，如果想要去距离城区较远的长隆度假区或者想要在各大批发市场里好好淘个货，最好再各拿出一天的时间。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">消费水平</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州是中国特大城市之一，经济发达，人口众多。消费水平也相对较高，处于国内一线水平。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">景点</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州仅有几处景点门票价格较贵，大部分景点门票都很便宜。像荔枝湾、越秀公园、沙面、石室圣心大教堂都不需要门票。中山纪念堂、陈家祠、白云山、兰圃门票仅需几块钱。各大可逛的商业街、小吃街也都能让游客免费转个遍。只有长隆度假区的各大主题公园和广州塔的门票较贵，价格在百元以上。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">餐饮</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州的餐饮消费水平高低兼备，适应各个阶层的游客就餐。在宝华路、上下九步行街上吃小吃，二三十元就可以吃的很饱。想要吃粤菜餐厅，广州也有人均几十块的老字号酒楼。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">若是喜爱优质服务，珠江新城沿线众多的奢华餐厅任你挑。若还不满足，坐落在广州塔几百米高空的旋转餐厅定能让你大快朵颐。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">住宿</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">广州住宿的选择多样，各档位的酒店都有。大多数游客都会选择住在上下九、北京路沿线，这两处的青年旅社及快捷酒店比较多，距离各景点间也较近。青旅床位费用在60元左右，标准酒店价格在350元左右。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">如果喜欢高档一些的酒店，珠江新城附近有很多奢华五星酒店，大多数都是外资名牌，一晚价格要超过千元。广州南部的长隆度假区也拥有自己的主题酒店，一晚价格在一千元左右。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">交通</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在广州游客的主要出行方式是地铁，便捷的轨道交通可以轻而易举的把游客送到各个景点。地铁票价从2-15元不等。如果仅在市区各景点游览，最多一天交通费用也就在20元左右。广州出租车的价格相对其他大城市来说要便宜一些，起步价仅为10元，2.5公里后每公里2块6。</p><div><br></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-11 19:37:32', '', '80', 'group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvayAWEmuAAIev-ksdo4161.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvVyAQMeMAAEcJjIqne8219.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvV2AA0xpAAD29wIjZms327.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvV-AEfAeAAH8l1SCe5s403.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvWGAAOFRAAGyiH9zFTk785.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvWSAHkUdAAFlJx93KC0870.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvWiAMBTFAAH7dndlT7w069.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvWyACRupAAMY13vWvcI887.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvW2Ad4BzAAFRkjyaznw901.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvXCAAaPbAAGR52XGyFo634.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440200', '240', '440000', '韶关', 'SG', 'S', '113.597307', '24.811496', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/c8d77b221d484d1abf3ff3cf973ebcdb.jpg', '丹霞山,南华寺,梅关古道,', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">韶关速览</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">韶关古称韶州，是“马坝人”的故乡，石峡文化的发祥地，有着2100多年的城市历史。历史上的韶州被誉为“岭南名郡”，孕育了以陈朝重臣侯安都、唐代名相张九龄、宋代名臣余靖、清代文学家廖燕为杰出代表的大批历史名人。佛教禅宗六祖惠能在韶州弘法37年，韶关南华寺因此成为禅宗的“南宗祖庭”。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">这里是粤北地区的经济中心，历史上也曾盛极一时；这里曾是岭南重镇，历经千载。在韶关，你可以在珠玑巷里追寻时光流逝下斑驳的历史，在丹霞山上赞叹大自热的神奇，在南华寺里感受六祖慧能的佛宗禅意，在梅关古道上看红梅傲雪，遥想当年虎踞龙盘，一夫当关万夫莫开的雄浑气势......</p><div class=\"figure\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 20px;\"><a href=\"http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/4E/D7/wKgBpVV1Dh6ARl-wAAO76b-8G5c76.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"http://c1-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/4E/D7/wKgBpVV1Dh6ARl-wAAO76b-8G5c76.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin-bottom: 8px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">韶关地图</div></div></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">消费水平</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">韶关的消费水平不是很高，一般用餐人均在20元左右，经济型住宿价格在150元上下，打车起步价7元。</p></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_3\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">充沛的雨量使韶关大地四季常青，全年都很适宜旅游。另外，丹霞山四季景色不同，最佳旅行季节是春天3-5月，秋天10-12月两季。</p></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_4\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">穿衣指南</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">韶关一般10月份左右就开始降温，12月份温度在8-18度之间。4月份左右开始回暖，出行时建议穿中等厚度毛衣，外面套厚外套，最好带上围巾，另外提示，爬山要选择舒适运动鞋。3、4月份，是韶关的梅雨季节，气温潮湿寒冷，出门最好带雨具，穿厚外套。7-8月天气较热，可穿薄纱、短裤，注意防晒。</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-07-14 13:47:52', '', '90', 'group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloV-iAMdxKAAEVPEmDEWA022.jpg', 'group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWuaAVmQmAAHJIq-uALM040.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWuiACRgSAALCD01kziI771.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWuuASCX8AAILLIBeanY685.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWu6AWxGOAAJgzqXReZA557.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWvGAJcYXAALkma2hViM045.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWvSAI0wDAAG04bxWt8Q987.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWwGAUG2cAAG33koB8Kk415.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWv2AcjmkAAI4DNcVjDg857.jpg,group1/M01/46/39/eBif6FloWv2AcN1GAAGhHQKXoys424.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440300', '240', '440000', '深圳', 'SZ', 'S', '114.057939', '22.543527', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/55337c4b257b4073acbae8b7fb02331e.jpg', '锦绣中华·民俗村,地王观光,深圳欢乐谷,', '0', '1', '2', '2', '1', '0', '1', '<section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳速览</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳一年四季如春，比邻香港，是一座新的不夜城，旅行购物的天堂。或许你是这个家园的繁忙居民，却又身在此城不识真面目之惑；或许你曾是这座城市的匆匆过客，对之投来惊鸿一瞥；或许，你从未抵达。那么，从此刻起，拿起路书，以一个崭新的视角，用眼睛去发现深圳之美，用心灵感受深圳之魅。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><a href=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/00/1B/wKgBpVVLN6mAf2lwAABqSXltWv074.jpeg\" _href=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/00/1B/wKgBpVVLN6mAf2lwAABqSXltWv074.jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(96, 127, 166); text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><img src=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/00/1B/wKgBpVVLN6mAf2lwAABqSXltWv074.jpeg\" _src=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/00/1B/wKgBpVVLN6mAf2lwAABqSXltWv074.jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(208, 208, 208); box-shadow: rgba(7, 1, 3, 0.4) 2px 2px 5px; color: inherit; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; height: auto !important;\"></a></p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳行政区划图最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">游深圳四季皆宜，尤以冬天和早春为最佳。8、9月份去深圳也是一个不错的选择，在夏日沙滩上漫步，大海里游泳，别有一番滋味。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">5-9月建议出门带雨具，穿短衣短袖即可，10月以后气温略有下降，可以穿抓绒外套，最冷的1月份可以穿厚大衣。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">消费水平</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳的消费较高，住宿、吃饭、交通价格和广州差不多，简单的一顿午餐一般人均20-30元左右，一般的住宿酒店价格在200-300元左右。</p><div><br></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '56', '2017-04-11 19:35:26', '', '91', 'group1/M01/40/94/eBif6Fjsvv-AFCiaAAHA4RpIkW4252.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvwWAUSHqAAFDux795Sg999.jpg,group1/M01/40/94/eBif6FjsvweAaszZAAE