: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">金湾区</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">珠海的很多岛屿都集中在这一区。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">珠海全年温暖湿润，冬无严寒，夏天不会特别热。3、4、10、12月是珠海的最佳旅游季节，适合到珠海的各岛屿上度假、探险和徒步。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">消费水平</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">珠海的消费水平没有广州那么高，但拱北一附近紧挨着澳门这一带的消费水平和一线城市的差不多，其他地方相对较低，一般快餐要10元左右，拱北附近快餐15元左右。公交车空调为2.5元，非空调为2元，出租车起步价10元。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; position: static; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">4-9月盛行东南季风，为雨季，全年的雨水都集中在这个时期，出门需要带雨具。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">10-3月盛行东北季风，为旱季。珠海的灾害性天气主要是台风和暴雨，个别年份冬季受寒潮低温影响。出注意防晒，多补充水分。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">台风出现的时间多在6-10月，年平均4次左右。严重影响珠海市的台风平均每年1次，暴雨有5次左右。</p><div><br></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-11 19:42:16', '', '97', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniZSAci8PAADyjB-vARY736.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniZuAQ5Z_AADSdYvD9io420.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniZ2Aa1wYAAEyIq6JEi4112.jpg,group1/M01/40/80/eBif6FjniZ-AGa77AAEJTqU9ymE283.jpg,group1/M01/40/80/eBif6FjniaCAZIMqAAH9uNU77mI586.jpg,group1/M01/40/80/eBif6FjniaOABsWNAAFmjow9kv0693.jpg,group1/M01/40/80/eBif6FjniaWAf9P5AAMVH1Wg4k4197.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440500', '240', '440000', '汕头', 'ST', 'S', '116.682014', '23.354125', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<div id=\"intro_15163\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">简介</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头市又叫“鮀城”，位于广东省的东南部，濒临南海，地处韩江、榕江、练江出海口，素有“岭东门户、华南要冲”的美称，是中国大陆唯一一个中心城区拥有内海的城市。汕头市拥有3个功能区（保税区，高新区，海湾新区），辖6个市辖区（金平区、濠江区、龙湖区、潮阳区、潮南区、澄海区）、1个县（南澳县）。<br>汕头是著名侨乡，华侨众多，与海外交往密切，是中国著名侨乡之一。自唐代开始就是中国海上丝绸之路的重要始发港，也是近代中国最大的移民口岸之一，海外的华侨、华人和港澳台同胞遍布世界40多个国家和地区，“有海水处就有华侨，有华侨处就有潮人”。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p></div><div id=\"intro_15164\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">历史</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头市区古为潮汕滨海冲积地。南宋末年，因战乱，闽南的十几万人从莆田移民现潮州府各地。在唐朝后期，北宋期间，南宋末期，元朝后期，明朝中后期的倭寇乱，都有很多福建莆田人迁移到此，移民原因是莆田人口过多和逃避因外军入侵导致的战乱，比如亦思法杭兵乱,南宋末年那一次规模最大。元代光华埠一带已有较大渔村，称厦岭。明初设蓬州守御千户所，嘉靖年间置澄海县时随属澄海。因是沙脊向海伸延，百姓设栅捕鱼，称沙汕头。清康熙年间建设汕头炮台。雍正年间简称汕头。1860年（咸丰十年）对外开市。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p></div><div id=\"intro_15168\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头盛夏虽高温而少酷暑，常受台风袭击；秋季凉爽干燥， 天气晴朗，冬无严寒，但有短期寒冷。7月中旬-8月初最热，温度在35℃-38℃。每年的4-5月和9-10月是汕头的最佳旅游时间，此时，温度适宜，十分适合出行。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p></div><div id=\"intro_15170\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">穿衣指南</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头春季多雨，出门建议带上雨具，穿长袖薄衫即可，夏日炎热，要注意防晒，冬天可以穿毛衣。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p></div><div id=\"intro_15178\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">语言</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">汕头的地方方言为潮汕话，和普通话差异很大，基本上听不懂，但当地人也都可以讲普通话，沟通不成问题。</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-07-14 11:59:31', '', '88', 'group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQOKALFbSAAD7ZU_o2Rg126.jpg', 'group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQXyAOjd9AADhi_j673E922.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQYGAJhHnAAKjK74zo3Q016.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQYKAaUAzAAHERCPsZFs652.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQYWAaFv7AAHYXcH9-f4435.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQYiAdQGiAAD_85dV23E196.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQYqALxhvAAHXf7t2RU0282.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQY-AQ1IXAALZBKOlHxc808.jpg,group1/M01/46/38/eBif6FloQZCAe3woAAEdTRrFcsM361.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440600', '240', '440000', '佛山', 'FS', 'F', '113.121643', '23.021374', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/22b5fc33257c415496a5899b033c31fa.jpg', '清晖园,南风古灶,南海观音寺,', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">佛山速览</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">佛山简称“禅”，位于广东省中部，是粤剧和岭南文化的发源地之一，素有粤剧之乡、南国陶都、武术之城的美誉，佛山现辖禅城区、顺德区、南海区、三水区、高明区五个区。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">这里是黄飞鸿、李小龙的故乡，是闻名的“武术之乡”，中国南派武术的主要发源地。佛山也是粤剧的发源地，有着独特的岭南文化气息，是以岭南文化为代表广府文化的兴盛之地，是珠三角的经济重地。荣耀千年的商贸名城，用生生不息的陶都圣火锻造出一座“敢为人先、崇文务实、通济和谐”的城市。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">佛山年平均气温在21.2-22.2℃间，气候温和，四季常绿，4-10月是佛山的最佳旅游时间。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">佛山气候温和，四季常绿，这里的冬季很短，一般持续2个月，最冷的温度出现在每年1月前后，温度在10℃左右，仪件毛衣，外面一件夹克即可，夏季可穿短衣、短裤，春秋可穿薄外套。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">消费水平</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">佛山的消费水平比广州略低，一般住宿的价格均价在150元左右，吃饭人均一般在20-30元左右。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\"><br></p><p></p>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-11 19:52:58', '', '79', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniMOANNEDAAUq-L7LHUY629.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniWmARjz5AAGqpqXeMQ4264.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniWuAcHtCAAJAls1_Fno722.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniW-AcccDAAobYZqmkc4362.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniXKAUGooAAD3X2Ukmm8343.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6FjniXiARmVdAAVFDkXtoNs473.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440700', '240', '440000', '江门', 'JM', 'J', '113.081415', '22.579089', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/66df8c1d3b5e47f79de4aef4c8b6f85c.jpg', '开平碉楼,自力村碉楼群,赤坎欧陆风情街,', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">简介</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">江门市是广东省中南部的地级市，因位于西江与其支流蓬江的会合处，江南烟墩山和江北蓬莱山对峙如门，故名江门，又称“四邑”、“五邑”。江门市现辖蓬江、江海、新会3区，代管台山、开平、恩平、鹤山4个县级市。其中新会、台山、开平、恩平四县俗称“四邑”，加上鹤山则称“五邑”，江门五邑被称为“中国第一侨乡”。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">历史</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">江门从元末明初形成墟集起，至今已有600多年历史。80年代实行市管县体制后逐渐成为五邑地区的政治、经济中心，全国著名侨乡的首府，也称为“中国侨都”。秦、汉时江门为番禺县地。三国后至民国前为新会县地。明、清时期，新会县属下的江门镇逐渐兴起，逐渐成为珠江三角洲的一个贸易中心，西江中下游一带的商品多在此地集散。清光绪二十八年开放为通商口岸。民国时与南海县佛山镇，增城县新塘镇，东莞县石龙镇并称为广东四大镇。建国后政府在江门投资建立门类齐全的工业体系，著名的企业有曾经是亚洲第二大糖厂的江门甘蔗化工厂，江门柴油机厂，江门造纸厂，江门船厂，江门无线电三厂，江门锁厂，江门电缆厂等，当时江门的工业产值跃居广东第三位。1983年，江门市定为省辖地级市，实行市管县新体制，并于2002年辖蓬江、江海、新会三区及台山、开平、鹤山、恩平四个县级市，辖区范围俗称“五邑”。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">江门夏季会有台风和暴雨，4-9月是汛期，7-9月是台风频发期，最佳旅游时间为春秋两季。每年3-5月是到开平看油菜花、碉楼的最好时节。10月是丰收季节，也是开平看碉楼的最佳时间。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">江门气候温暖湿润多雨，终年无雪，年平均气温全区均在22℃左右，夏季较热最高气温38℃。，穿短衣、短裤即可，注意防晒，4-9月多雨，出门最好带雨伞，冬天最低气温5℃，可穿厚的保暖外套。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">语言</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">江门市各市区之间通用广州话，各市区内均使用五邑话，在客家人聚居的地方，使用客家方言。随着经济的发展，普通话也成了较为通用的语言。来江门旅行的话，用普通话做日常交流是没问题的。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">　</p><p></p>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-15 16:39:14', '', '83', 'group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx29uAJX53AAFQWgHzIeE086.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2-GAeC6oAAFn_gu4E88623.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2-OAfuoqAAFI0IZn_fw971.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2-aAWJFzAAD5_JxsGXo698.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2-qAQJVMAADhNBDRafs476.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2-yAN5I7AAHqkgs6WrE697.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2--AYxOSAAFyZRC4-CE718.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2_OAdrIBAAF6sLYAkcc649.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2_qAKuXsAAGm2hwS6lw258.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjx2_iAB62tAAHXCXHBcCk195.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440800', '240', '440000', '湛江', 'ZJ', 'Z', '110.359414', '21.270703', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/a7bf48fd054a4c0bb5bfcf99a6452ad8.jpg', '湖光岩,东海岛,特呈岛,', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;\"><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: relative; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">简介</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">湛江简称“湛”，旧称“广州湾”（Kwangchouwan）、别称“港城”，湛江由一个半岛，30多个海岛组成，被湛江湾和雷州湾两个蓝色海湾环抱，湛江湾南有东海岛、硇洲岛、南屏岛，中有特呈岛和东山头岛，东有南三岛，构成“一湾多岸”的海湾格局，是一座“海在城中、城在海中、城中有岛、岛立城中”生态海湾型海滨城市。湛江市位于中国大陆的最南端，包括雷州半岛全部和半岛以北一部分。东濒南海，南隔琼州海峡与大特区海南省相望，西临北部湾，西北与广西壮族自治区的合浦、博白、陆川县毗邻，东北与本省茂名市属茂南区、茂港区及化州市接壤。市区位于雷州半岛东北部。现辖吴川市、雷州市、廉江市（3个县级市）和徐闻县、遂溪县（2县），以及赤坎区、霞山区、坡头区、麻章区、湛江市经济技术开发区（5区）。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">湛江气候具有常年高温、台风频繁，夏秋多雨，冬春干旱的特点，一般，在湛江11月份开始后，才会比较凉快些，外出旅游最适宜不过。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">湛江夏天穿短袖、短衫即可，冬天可以外加一件长外套，注意护肤补水。夏秋两季出门建议带雨具。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">语言</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">湛江有很多方言，雷州半岛讲的是闽南语系的方言——黎话。廉江大多地区讲的是客家方言——涯话。湛江市区和吴川讲的是粤语吴化片白话（类似化州的口音），这些方言和普通话有很大差别，外地人基本上听不懂，但当地大部分人都会讲普通话，虽然不是很标准，但沟通基本上没有问题。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">　</p></section>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-15 17:21:23', '', '0', 'group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5cmANiGoAAENyw0U4nw877.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5c-ARktWAAEnHl_i-D0474.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5dGAZU-cAADE-a_HRqk724.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5dKAGpr0AAEHobFA8sU919.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5dWAPlB7AAE_DDh-KfM773.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx5deAQxUwAAG_2vqOxgk391.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('440900', '240', '440000', '茂名', 'MM', 'M', '110.925466', '21.662725', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;\"><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">简介</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">茂名位于广东省西南部，鉴江中游，茂名是中国华南地区最大的石化基地，为中国南方重要的石化生产出口基地和广东省的能源基地。荔枝、香蕉、龙眼等“岭南佳果”驰名中外，是“中国最大的水果生产基地”，水产养殖享誉盛名，是“中国罗非鱼之都”。茂名有山有水有温泉有美食，是吃货的天堂，休闲的好去处，旅游的不二选择。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">四季皆宜，春秋最佳。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">建议游玩天数</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">1天</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">当地气候</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">亚热带季风性湿润气候</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">语言</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">粤语、涯话、黎话、海话等</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">　</p></section>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-15 17:02:53', '', '85', 'group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4XCAPWTFAAE2kziQk-c787.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4XKAGRJZAAEjXwi7WlU244.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4YaAFeLSAADsFw696Rs884.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4XuAIrphAADwebuEvzc222.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4XyAUlI8AAD8eaVn4uI453.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4X6ATA-rAAEta5TkFPk731.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4YSASveqAAIV6JtlHd8811.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4YmAOncfAAD6gnQd6iw932.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4ZeAK-xfAAFRlSGr4hI849.jpg,group1/M01/40/A8/eBif6Fjx4ZmAXoNjAADdh91dOJg445.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('441200', '240', '440000', '肇庆', 'ZQ', 'Z', '112.465091', '23.047191', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:16px;\"><h1 class=\"h1\" style=\"font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); float: left; line-height: 1.6em;\"><section data-role=\"outer\" label=\"Powered by 135editor.com\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">肇庆速览</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">肇庆市位于中国华南，隶属于广东省，西靠桂东南，珠江主干流西江穿境而过，北回归线横贯其中。背枕北岭，面临西江，上控苍梧，下制南海，为粤西咽喉之地。肇庆现辖端州、鼎湖2个区、和广宁、怀集、封开、德庆4县，代管高要、四会2个县级市。</p><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">肇庆是广东最美的城市，是岭南土著文化的发祥地，是中国的砚都，这里有着辉煌的历史和文化，也有着无以伦比的绝美山水.....</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">最佳旅行时间</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">肇庆属南亚热带季风气候。年平均气温21.2℃，降雨多集中在4-9月，7月份温度最高，平均在28.7℃，肇庆的冬天不是很冷，夏天也不是很热，一年四季都是很好的旅游季节。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">穿衣指南</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">肇庆一年四季温度都不是很冷，7、8月份是气温最高的时候，穿短袖、短衫即可，12-1月稍冷，穿一件厚外套即可，春秋时节可穿薄衫。</p><section class=\"_135editor\" data-id=\"t3\" style=\"position: static; border: 0px none; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><section style=\"margin:10px 0px;\"><section class=\"assistant\" style=\"margin: 5px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(248, 122, 122); box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</section><section style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;\"><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #F87A7A;\">消费水平</span></p></section></section></section><p style=\"line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify; color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;\">肇庆消费水平和广东省其他城市比属于中等偏下，一般一顿饭人均在20元左右，住宿的话一般150元左右可以住的很好。</p></section></h1></section>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-15 17:04:22', '', '95', 'group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6FjxzlmADpX0AAEVUY19DiI681.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6Fjxzl2ANsQNAAClA6sagZA828.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6FjxzmCAcecFAAXNUaIIp5I325.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6FjxzmGAUd0sAACeASkvEsk708.jpg,group1/M01/40/A7/eBif6FjxzmSAdZPTAAejNZAzm1I207.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('441300', '240', '440000', '惠州', 'HZ', 'H', '114.415612', '23.112381', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/17cfedc57dcb40358e267a76be4ecb4d.jpg', '惠州西湖,广东罗浮山风景名胜区,巽寮湾,', '0', '1', '0', '2', '3', '0', '1', '<div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">惠州速览</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州旧称惠阳地区（简称惠阳），在古代即有“岭南名郡”、“粤东门户”、“半城山色半城湖”之称。拥有TCL、德赛、华阳等大型本土国有（控股）企业集团以及侨兴、富绅等本土民营企业集团，数码、石化是惠州的两大经济支柱。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州市位于广东省中南部，广东三大水系之一的东江及其支流西枝江横贯境内，现辖惠城区、惠阳区2个区、惠东县、博罗县、龙门县3个县，大亚湾区1个国家级经济技术开发区和仲恺区1个国家级高新技术产业开发区。</p><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州是客家人的重要聚居地，叶挺、廖仲恺等人出生在这里，宋代文豪苏东坡曾生活在这里。西子湖畔，似乎还能感受到苏轼谪贬后的惆怅情怀；罗浮山下，依然可见昔日香客络绎不绝的景象；那些隐匿在山野中的古村落，青砖黛瓦中显露出一种颓败的凄美，掉了色的雕花镂空在余晖下更显落寞，雕刻出历史的印记；海湾在无尽的大海边曲折蜿蜒，毓秀的山水继续着四季轮回的交替……这里便是惠州，只有用心去仔细体会，你才能发现它的美好。</p><div class=\"figure\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); line-height: 20px;\"><a href=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/E0/C5/wKgBpVWBP8-ALwGWAACQmUwUvZY60.jpeg\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"点击查看原图\" style=\"color: rgb(153, 153, 153); text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"http://c2-q.mafengwo.net/s8/M00/E0/C5/wKgBpVWBP8-ALwGWAACQmUwUvZY60.jpeg\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin-bottom: 8px; max-width: 100%;\"></a><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州行政区划图</div></div></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州年平均气温22℃，气候温和，冬季寒冷时最低气温13℃，7、8月份惠州降雨较多，9、10月份天气晴朗，是出游的好时机。</p></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_3\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">穿衣指南</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州气候温和，即使在最冷的冬季穿一件长袖厚外套即可，7-8月较热，可穿短衣短裤。</p></div><div class=\"part\" id=\"wiki_part_4\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">消费水平</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">惠州的消费较低，一般经济型住宿在200元左右，午餐消费人均10-20元，打车起步价7元。</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-11 19:21:36', '', '82', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh8qAW6ucAAGaDdnHAtM812.jpg', 'group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh7eAafEUAAGNP6iNASg632.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh7qAG9DFAACvMb8MQWA942.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh72ARgYIAAJi_WRC-tk376.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh76AMmMdAAFwCZTDv-M108.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh8CAek1nAAD6ih7dL7s428.jpg,group1/M01/40/7F/eBif6Fjnh86APVRjAAFRJ0eU3Rw974.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('441400', '240', '440000', '梅州', 'MZ', 'M', '116.122022', '24.288742', '', '', '0', '0', '0', '2', '0', '0', '1', '<div id=\"intro_unstrt-desc\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\"><br></div><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">简介</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">梅州市隶属中国广东省，是中国著名的四乡——“文化之乡、华侨之乡、足球之乡、客家之乡”，同时还享山歌之乡、金柚之乡等美称。梅州是客家人最主要的集散中心和聚居地，是全世界客家华侨的祖籍地和精神家园。同时，梅州市自然景观和人文景点众多，包括千佛塔、人境庐、归读公园、叶剑英纪念园、中国客家博物馆等景点吸引力全世界的客家人及游人的到来。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelseason\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti; widows: 1;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word