; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">兰银官话、中原官话</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-21 17:39:55', '', '0', 'group1/M01/41/44/eBif6Fj50hSAVfGoAAGDK5w4lj4125.jpg', 'group1/M01/41/44/eBif6Fj501SAO1e_AASMyBe4jI4091.jpg,group1/M01/41/44/eBif6Fj501qALN2IAAH4rXvET1k322.jpg,group1/M01/41/44/eBif6Fj5016AInCvAAvEjfe9ouE824.jpg,group1/M01/41/44/eBif6Fj502SADOokAApWhgjc9G0797.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('620500', '240', '620000', '天水', 'TS', 'T', '105.724896', '34.581177', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/222ed8ea5b634e739bdb14aea6836eb7.jpg', '麦积山石窟,仙人崖,伏羲庙,', '0', '0', '0', '5', '0', '0', '1', '<div id=\"intro_unstrt-desc\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">简介</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">天水是国家历史文化名城，羲皇始创八卦，故天水又被称为“易学之都”。境内四季分明，气候宜人，物产富饶，素有西北“小江南”之称。同时境内文物古迹甚多，现有国家和盛市级重点保护文物169处，其中大地湾遗址保存有大量新石器时代早期及仰韶文化珍品；国内唯一有伏羲塑像的天水伏羲庙，雕梁画栋，古柏成林；中国四大石窟之一的麦积山石窟，号称“东方雕塑馆”，有不同时期古佛7730余尊，并与大像山、水帘洞、拉梢寺、木梯寺等共同组成了古丝绸之路东段的“石窟艺术走廊”。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelseason\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">四季皆宜，夏秋最佳。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-traveltime\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">建议游玩天数</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">2天</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelweather\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">当地气候</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">夏无酷暑，冬无严寒。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travellanguage\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">语言</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">天水话</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-24 17:11:57', '', '0', 'group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wFGAQvG3AAI0kCSmKbY979.jpg', 'group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wTiADRx8AASsYuigg2s819.jpg,group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wT2ARRB_AAH_YBtVEYQ467.jpg,group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wUGAIHfgAAQ2Pp6T6XY591.jpg,group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wUWAV2q1AAG5PMOM-pY430.jpg,group1/M01/41/CE/eBif6Fj9wUqAdGDkAAKWtx8pU7w639.jpg');
