55, 157, 0);\">语言</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">中原官话关中方言西海固片区</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-21 15:37:30', '', '0', 'group1/M01/41/41/eBif6Fj5sgKAQxZHAAIQGb0hOI4370.jpg', 'group1/M01/41/42/eBif6Fj5tpWAQWfrAAD_qcy7nuU092.jpg,group1/M01/41/42/eBif6Fj5tpiAd1R4AAD-E6dv8GQ112.jpg,group1/M01/41/42/eBif6Fj5tpuALke8AAG5sjX7x7s674.jpg,group1/M01/41/42/eBif6Fj5tp6ALlJLAAFcPqIZqHA461.jpg,group1/M01/41/42/eBif6Fj5tqOATNjgAAGWdnESe-o902.jpg');
