: break-word;\">维吾尔语</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-25 14:29:18', '', '0', 'group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-69-ANhX6AAFZsErB5ww110.jpg', 'group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-7JqAY4QbAAKKfGNmp0E229.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-7J2ANyMgAAO8uU8XMjE142.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-7KCAFwj3AAH3o8i_RuE723.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-7KOAHMzAAAM1AaeKigk198.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-7KeAd4oNAAMSI0q3DB4709.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('652300', '240', '650000', '昌吉', 'CJ', 'C', '87.267532', '44.014435', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/27929b2e2e8e4b39b2f32561b26dc2dc.jpg', '龟山岛,国立传统艺术中心,南方澳渔港,', '0', '0', '0', '5', '0', '0', '1', '<div id=\"intro_unstrt-desc\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">简介</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">昌吉回族自治州新疆维吾尔自治区的下辖行政区之一，地处天山北麓、准噶尔盆地东南缘，东邻哈密地区，西接石河子市，南与吐鲁番地区、巴音郭楞蒙古自治州毗连，北与塔城、阿勒泰地区接壤，东北与蒙古国交界，是古代举世闻名的“丝绸之路”新北道通往中亚、欧洲诸国的必经之路。昌吉旅游资源独具特色。有著名的国家级旅游风景区--高山湖泊天池、有始建于汉代的西域历史名城北庭都护府遗址、有距今3000年历史的呼图壁康家石门子原始生殖崇拜岩画、有亚洲最大的恐龙化石发掘地、东方最大的古森林化石群及鸣沙山、原始胡杨林等人文和自然奇观。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelseason\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">四季皆宜，秋季最佳。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-traveltime\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">建议游玩天数</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">1天</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelweather\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">当地气候</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">大陆性干旱气候</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travellanguage\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">语言</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">新疆话</p></div>', '0', '2015-05-12 16:16:02', '', '2017-04-25 14:24:05', '', '0', 'group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-6imASem6AAHPI_pufDQ728.jpg', 'group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-62WATpjPAARWaZ5xDV0119.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-62eAeEhKAAHGSKpmSBE538.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-62uAAJQbAAUBbd6Kpig209.jpg,group1/M01/41/D1/eBif6Fj-62-AM5-fAAKNH3D5M9k142.jpg');
INSERT INTO `sys_city` VALUES ('652700', '240', '650000', '博尔塔拉', 'BETL', 'B', '82.066363', '44.906039', 'https://imgb.mofangx.com/test/49af75aaa18942d093a70443cddc7230.jpg', '三义木雕博物馆,龙腾断桥,飞牛牧场,', '0', '0', '0', '5', '0', '0', '1', '<div id=\"intro_unstrt-desc\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">简介</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">博尔塔拉位于中国新疆维吾尔自治区西北边缘，北部与哈萨克斯坦共和国接壤，有“中国西部第一门户”之称。博尔塔拉是蒙古自治州，但除了蒙古族，同时还聚居着35个少数民族，包括维吾尔、哈萨克、回等民族。博尔塔拉旅游资源极其丰富，有满目白雪蓝天的赛里木湖、我国西北最大的怪石群落之一的怪石峪、避暑胜地——哈日图热格、神秘壮观的草原石人、新疆第一大盐水湖艾比湖以及诸多温泉，在这里，你会惊叹于大自然的鬼斧神工，感恩上天的恩赐。</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-travelseason\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; border-left: 2px solid rgb(238, 238, 238); font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); line-height: 20px; font-family: Arial, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB W3&quot;, SimSun, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, STHeiti;\"><div class=\"h2\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px -22px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); height: 29px; line-height: 28px; font-size: 18px; border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 157, 0);\">最佳旅行时间</div><p style=\"margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0px; word-wrap: break-word;\">6-10月</p></div><div id=\"intro_unstrt-traveltime\" class=\"part\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 50px; padding: 0px 0px 1px 20